data.text: @RDT_anantapur So Happy and... RDT is deserved to get more awards like this... Congrats team💐💐💐❤.

@RDT_anantapur అంతర్జాతీయ మహిళా దినోత్సవం సందర్భంగా లీడ్ ఇండియా ఫౌండేషన్ వారు,RDT మహిళా సాధికారత డైరెక్టర్ శ్రీమతి విశాల ఫెర్రర్ గారికి అవార్డు అందజేసిన సందర్భంగా శుభాకాంక్షలు. From :-పరమేశ్వరావు, గుంటూరు.🌹🌹🌹🌹🌹🌹

She received the award from Shri Arikapudi Gandhi, Telangana State Legislative Assembly member (MLA), who attended the event as the Chief Guest. Actors Jeevitha Rajashekar and Neha Saxena were also among the attendees.

The event which took place at Shilpakalavedika in Hyderabad has attempted to set a record for recognizing 111 women in 110 minutes. The Lead India Foundation organized it in partnership with the Government of Telangana, GHMC and Telangana Tourism Department. https://t.co/waibwm3BjS
